== Homosapien Osliner Edit ==

This is my proposal for Lucid metacity. The theme is based on Homosapien, but uses the selected background color, and has many tweeks like the gradient, the little shine on the top, and edited  buttons.

On the screenshot it is the default lucid gtk and colors.
